                  <summary><p>A multi-text (possibly a composite in fact) manuscript containing 6 works attributed to Akattiyar:
<list rend="numbered">
  <item>The <title xml:lang="ta">Vaittiyam</title>, in 300 <foreign xml:lang="ta">cūttiram</foreign>s (U3).</item>
<item>The <title xml:lang="ta">Paṟpavakai</title> (U4).</item>
<item>The <title xml:lang="ta">TBC</title> (portion of <title xml:lang="ta">Paṟpavakai</title> or  <title xml:lang="ta">Tīṣṣāviti</title>?)  (U5).</item>
<item>The <title xml:lang="ta">Vaittiyam</title>, in 50 <foreign xml:lang="ta">cūttiram</foreign>s (U6).</item>
<item>The <title xml:lang="ta">Paṣṣiṇi</title> (U7).</item>
<item>The <title xml:lang="ta">Aṣṭakarmam</title> (U8).</item>
<item>A series of 10 <foreign xml:lang="ta">Pūcāviti</foreign>s (U10).</item>
</list></p>
<p>Description based on the examination of the original manuscript (December 2021).</p>
   <p>Dimensions assessed at the time of examination.</p>      </summary>
                  
